    <h2 class="text-primary-dark">Introduction</h2>
    <p>At NebulaTextbook one of our main priorities is the privacy of our students. This Cookie Policy document contains types of information that is collected and recorded by NebulaTextbook and how we use it.</p>

    <h2 class="text-primary-dark">What Are Cookies?</h2>
    <p>Cookies are small files that are placed on your device when you visit a website. They are widely used to make websites work or function more efficiently, as well as to provide information to the site owners.</p>

    <h2 class="text-primary-dark">How We Use Cookies</h2>
    <p>NebulaTextbook uses cookies for several reasons, including:</p>
    <ul class="list-group">
        <li class="list-group-item">To enhance the functionality and performance of the website.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">To track and analyze how students interact with the website and to improve user experience.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item">To remember your preferences and settings for future visits.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-primary-dark">Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
    <p>We use the following types of cookies on our site:</p>
    <ul class="list-group">
        <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> These cookies are necessary for the operation of our website. They allow you to navigate the website and use its features.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Performance Cookies:</strong> These cookies collect information about how users interact with our website, such as which pages are most frequently visited.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Functionality Cookies:</strong> These cookies allow the website to remember choices you make (such as language preferences) and provide enhanced features.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-primary-dark">Managing Cookies</h2>
    <p>You have the right to decide whether to accept or reject cookies. You can manage cookie preferences by adjusting your browser settings. If you choose to disable cookies, some features of the website may not function properly, and you may experience reduced functionality.</p>
    <p>Most web browsers allow you to control cookies through their settings. To learn more about how to manage cookies, visit the <a href="https://www.aboutcookies.org/" target="_blank" class="text-primary-dark">About Cookies website</a>.</p>

    <h2 class="text-primary-dark">Consent</h2>
    <p>By using our website, you consent to the use of cookies in accordance with this Cookie Policy. If you do not agree to the use of cookies, please disable them as described above or refrain from using the site.</p>

